name: Bootstrike.Com
overview:
We are committed to assisting small to medium companies establish an online website professionally. Our number one priority in developing the site is that they are usable, accessible and professional.

Your website is the first place most prospective customers go to when they want more information on your products and services. The reason is simple - It is the quickest and most convenient avenue to obtain more information on your products and services.

Studies have shown (link to external pdf) that a website has only 50ms to make a good impression. Which is why, it is important that your website makes a good FIRST impression of your company to your potential customers. We create professional visually-pleasant looking sites to ensure your visitors get the good 50ms impression you deserve.

Our affordable packages are designed to cater to most of our client’s requirements. Customised packages are also available. We strive to be the best through customer satisfaction.
